text: The 2020 United States presidential election in Alaska took place on Tuesday, November 3, 2020, as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Incumbent PresidentDonald Trump and his running mate Vice President Mike Pence had won 3 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:2020s in Alaska
title: 2020 United States presidential election in Alaska
